data.description: Hurry over to Terrace Meadows where this charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home is nestled in at 111 Goldenrod Lane in the heart of Beebe. Along with the endearing curb appeal, this home has only had 1 owner and is in tip top shape! Upon entry, you will find a very welcoming open split floor plan with a cozy living room. Step into the kitchen you will find ample cabinet and counter space, a pantry, & room for a dining room table! The primary suite has a considerable amount of space, a window allowing for the perfect amount of natural light.  The primary bathroom has a massive walk-in closet, a ton of shelving for linens, & a vanity spot to top it off! Both guest bedrooms are large in size and have great closet space. Heading out back you will find a host-ready, oversized flat backyard!  Call today for your very own private showing! This is home!
